0x7302DBCF.name: GET_PLAYER_IDENTIFIER
0x7302DBCF.description:
To get the number of identifiers, use [GET_NUM_PLAYER_IDENTIFIERS](#\_0xFF7F66AB)

To get a specific type of identifier, use [GET_PLAYER_IDENTIFIER_BY_TYPE](#\_0xA61C8FC6)
0x7302DBCF.resultsDescription: Returns the identifier at the specific index, if out of bounds returns `null`
